deck: Christophe Coronas, who publishes under the name Cecil, is a comic book artist from Bordeaux. After his studies in fine arts, Ccil worked a librarian, graphic artist and illustrator. His debut comic 'L'Empreinte des Chimres' was created under his real name Coronas, and was published by Vents d'Ouest in 1990. In 1999, he started the series 'Le Rseau Bombyce' with Eric Corbeyran at Les Humanodes Associs. The third and final book was published in 2010. He made the children's comic 'Contes et Rcits de Ma
